author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Utenos Trikotažas Group Sales In 2017 Up At Eur 22.6 Million
text:
Feb 28 (Reuters) - UTENOS TRIKOTAZAS AB:
* UTENOS TRIKOTAŽAS GROUP ACHIEVES 13.4% GROWTH IN 2017 * SAYS GROUP‘S PRE-TAX PROFIT FOR 2017 WAS EUR 435 THOUSAND
* SAYS SALES INCREASED 15% IN 2017 TO EUR 22.6 MILLION, * SAYS ‍SALES OF PRODUCTS AND SERVICES FOR COMPANY INCREASED 15% IN 2017 TO EUR 22.6 MILLION​
* SAYS FY 2017 CO‘S PRE-TAX PROFIT FOR YEAR WAS EUR 2.25 MILLION, COMPARED WITH EUR 674 THOUSAND IN 2016 Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage: (Gdynia Newsroom)
